OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FTemperatures climbing further,
OL,7,Fpotentially reaching very hot levels
OL,8,Fby day, with very warm nights. Mainly
OL,9,Ffine with further sunshine, though
OL,10,Fisolated thunderstorms may develop
OL,11,Flater on Thursday and into Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
